		<div class="intro">
			<p>Digital Education Strategies (DES) at The Chang School is a leader in providing online learning solutions, creating web applications, and sharing expertise in technology-enhanced education. We collaborate with educators and industry partners to develop relevant, high-quality online and blended courses for a diverse range of learners.</p>
		</div>
