			<div class="column left">
				<h2>Our Offerings</h2>
				<p>Today, The Chang School delivers over 400 online courses, including around 300 degree-credit online and hybrid courses, four part-time degree online and blended programs, 23 fully online certificates, and 22 blended certificates.</p>
				<p>In collaboration with The Chang School’s academic program areas, we have developed the following fully and partially online certificates and programs.</p>
			</div>
