	<article class="testimonials">
		<h2>Our eLearning Initiatives</h2>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/bse.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>BSE</h3>
			<p>The Chang School is working with BSE (formerly Bombay Stock Exchange Ltd.) to design a training program for the effective delivery of a hybrid curriculum on workplace intercultural communication skills.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/cis_logo.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Council of International Schools</h3>
			<p>The Chang School collaborated with CIS to develop  interactive hybrid learning modules on evidence-based report writing for CIS assessors, to support them during the process of accreditation. The Chang School also designed an orientation module for CIS facilitators on effective facilitation of online and hybrid learning. </p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/fcac.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Financial Consumer Agency of Canada (FCAC)</h3>
			<p>By deploying its expert resources in multimedia production and design, The Chang School, in partnership with the FCAC, launched a series of free eLearning modules to help Canadians boost their financial knowledge.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/lakedevo.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Lake Devo</h3>
			<p>A highly adaptable online role play environment and presentation tool designed by Digital Education Strategies at The Chang School of Continuing Education. </p>
			<p><a href="https://lakedevo.ryerson.ca/" target="de">Learn more about LakeDevo application...</a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/lsuc.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Law Practice Program (LPP)</h3>
			<p>The Chang School is supporting Ryerson’s LPP to deliver a unique articling program using interactive, web-based collaboration tasks that replicate the experience of working in a law firm.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/pearson.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Pearson Canada Inc.</h3>
			<p>The Chang School is working with Pearson Canada Inc. to design, develop, and deliver a customized, interactive training program on the essentials of instructional design.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/mooc.jpg" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Digital Accessibility Teaching and Learning Resources</h3>
			<p>Series of practical online courses and interactive open textbooks aimed at raising awareness of digital accessibility, improving understanding and implementation of the requirements of Digital Accessibility.</p>
			<p><a href="https://de.ryerson.ca/wa/" target="de">Learn more about digital accessibility courses...</a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/sg2.jpg" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Serious Game: A Home Visit</h3>
			<p>A virtual interactive game developed in collaboration with nurses and professors from George Brown College, Centennial College and Ryerson University.</p>
			<p><a href="https://de.ryerson.ca/games/nursing/mental-health/" target="de">Learn more about Home Visit game...</a></p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/talo.jpg" alt=""></div>
			<h3>Teaching Adult Learners Online (TALO)</h3>
			<p>A professional development program for online teaching and course design anchored in research and expertise gained through years of experience designing and delivering digital education at The Chang School of Continuing Education.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/uwi.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>University of the West Indies</h3>
			<p>This partnership with the University of the West Indies provided students in 12 Caribbean countries with access to a high-quality online Bachelor of Science in Nursing (BScN) program.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="initiative clearfix">
			<div class="thumbnail"><img src="_/img/initiatives/game_research.png" alt=""></div>
			<h3>The Art of Serious Games</h3>
			<p>A hands-on workshop for designing educational games.</p>
			<p><a href="https://de.ryerson.ca/games/research/" target="de">Learn more about designing educational games...</a></p>
		</div>
